TopicTitle: How many planets & moons have u landed & get back safely in same trip. (NO MODS!)

Articles.Content:
Mun, Minmus, Duna, Ike, Gilly, Laythe is my list. And something to be added it must be mission with one or more kerbals!

So my number is 6.

Edited October 20, 2013 by TUFOM

Eeloo, Moho, Mun, Minmus, Duna, and Dres.

NO MODS 4 LYFE

In KSP v0.21, all planets and moons except Eve. I landed in Eve many times but I've only been using mod I could launch after from Eve's surface.

In KSP v0.22, I visited Mun, Minmus, Duna and Ike.
